Support daddy Tamers by joining my patreon https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345

comments.text: Tamers, I really hope you keep making all of these videos. For me, the audience you serve isn't as large as I think you deserve, but I hope that never dissuades you from pumping out this actually funny shit. Your stuff makes me laugh harder than most things I see, and I would be fucking devastated if you stopped. I don't know if you're employed as an actual creative writer, but you should. The way  your jokes and stories are structured never fail to fucking kill me. You've captured the humor of this incredibly niche sub culture to a tee, to the point where it seems tailor made to make a weirdo like me laugh. So please, never stop what you're doing. I can't find this anywhere else.
